==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Subtriplicate
<hw>Sub*trip"li*cate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Math.)</fld>
<def>Expressed by the cube root; -- said especially of ratios.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Subtriplicate ratio</b></col>, <cd>the ratio of the cube
root; thus, the <xex>subtriplicate ratio</xex> of <it>a</it> to
<it>b</it> is ⟦cuberoot⟧<it>a</it> to ⟦cuberoot⟧<it>b</it>, or
⟦cuberoot⟧<fract><it>a</it>/<it>b</it></fract>.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Subtropical</ent>⟦br⟧
